    <section class="full-cover bg-faded" role="region" id="svg" aria-labelledby="title-svg">
      <div class="container">

        <h2 class="full-cover-title" id="title-svg">SVG</h2>

        <div class="text-right to-top">
          <a href="#totop" class="link-ts"><span>To Top</span></a>
        </div>

        <div class="row">

          <div class="col-md-7">

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Checklist - Deque</h3>

                <h4 class="heading-s">SVG as <code>img src</code></h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>All SVG <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> be set to <code>role="img"</code>.</li>
                  <li>All informative or actionable SVG <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have meaningful, concise alternative text (via <code>alt</code>, <code>aria-label</code>, or <code>aria-labelledby</code>).</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Inline SVGs</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>All <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be set to <code>role="img"</code>.</li>
                  <li>All informative or actionable <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have meaningful, concise alternative text (via <code>&lt;title&gt;</code> element).</li>
                  <li>The alternative text (<code>&lt;title&gt;</code>) of an <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> element <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be programmatically associated with the <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> element via <code>aria-labelledby</code>.</li>
                  <li>All text within the image that needs to be spoken by a screen reader <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be associated with the <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> element using <code>aria-labelledby</code>.</li>
                  <li>The total number of characters of alt text associated with the <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> element <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD NOT</span> exceed 250 characters.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Embedded SVGs</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>An SVG object <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD NOT</span> be embedded via <code>&lt;object&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code>.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Complex Alternative Text</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>Complex <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> images <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have meaningful, concise alternative text AND <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have a more complete long description.</li>
                  <li>A <code>&lt;desc&gt;</code> element <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be used to provide a detailed description of a complex <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> if it is not provided in any other way.</li>
                  <li>The <code>&lt;desc&gt;</code> attribute of an <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> element <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be programmatically associated with the <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> element (via <code>aria-labelledby</code>).</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Text in SVGs</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>Text within <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> be eliminated OR <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> be kept to a minimum.</li>
                  <li>All <code>&lt;text&gt;</code> elements inside <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be referenced in the alternative text of the <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> element, or in a long description.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">SVG Color Contrast</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>SVG images <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> include a base background color behind the important parts of the image, at a minimum.</li>
                  <li>SVG images <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> be styled to ensure compatibility with Windows High Contrast Mode</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Animated SVG Content</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>SVG animations <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> use JavaScript, rather than the <code>&lt;animate&gt;</code> element.</li>
                  <li>SVG animations <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> not flash or blink at a rate of 3 times per second or more.</li>
                  <li>SVG animations <span class="badge badge-danger">MUST NOT</span> auto-play for more than 5 seconds.</li>
                  <li>SVG animations <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> allow users to pause the animation.</li>
                  <li>SVG animations <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD NOT</span> distract the user from the main purpose of the web content.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Interactive SVGs</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>Interactive <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> objects <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be fully keyboard-accessible. </li>
                  <li>Interactive <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> objects <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be fully touchscreen-accessible.</li>
                  <li>Interactive <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> objects <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> communicate the applicable name, role, and value of controls, events, and semantic elements within the <code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> object.<br>
                  </li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Download Summary & Checklist</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-linklist">
                  <li><a href="https://github.com/team-a11y/A11YPortal/blob/master/docs/summary-checklists/Images%2C%20Canvas%2C%20SVG%2C%20and%20Other%20Non-Text%20Content%20-%20Design%20-%20Summary%20and%20Checklist.pdf" class="link-ts"><span>Images, Canvas, SVG, and Other Non-Text Content PDF</span></a></li>
                </ul>

              </div>
              <div>
                <a href="https://dequeuniversity.com/class/images2/svg/" class="link-plug-on">
                  <span class="icon icon-college icon-xl icon-gray-dark mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></span> SVG - Deque University</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Tips & Tricks</h3>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>Preferred approach: Basic <code>&lt;svg&gt;...&lt;svg&gt;</code></li>
                  <li>Use <code>&lt;title&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;desc&gt;</code> and <code>aria-labelledby</code> for maximum accessibility</li>
                </ul>

              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="col-md-5">

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Resources</h3>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Specifications</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-linklist">
                  <li><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/graphics-aria-1.0/" class="link-ts"><span>WAI-ARIA Graphics Module</span></a></li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Examples</h4>
                <p>None documented</p>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Miscellaneous</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-linklist">
                  <li><a href="https://css-tricks.com/mega-list-svg-information/" class="link-ts"><span>A Compendium of SVG Information</span></a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Practice</h3>

                <h4 class="heading-s">WCAG Annotations</h4>
                <p>None documented</p>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Design Annotations</h4>
                <p>None documented</p>

              </div>
              <div>
                <a href="https://github.com/team-a11y/A11YPortal" class="link-plug-on">
                  <span class="icon icon-college icon-xl icon-gray-dark mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></span> Good / Bad - Github</a>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="full-cover bg-grey" role="region" id="icon-fonts" aria-labelledby="title-icon-fonts">
      <div class="container">

        <h2 class="full-cover-title" id="title-icon-fonts">Icon Fonts</h2>

        <div class="text-right to-top">
          <a href="#totop" class="link-ts"><span>To Top</span></a>
        </div>

        <div class="row">

          <div class="col-md-7">

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Checklist - Deque</h3>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Icon Fonts</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>Informative icon fonts without accompanying visible text <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> be assigned <code>role="img"</code>.</li>
                  <li>Informative icon fonts without accompanying visible text <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have a text alternative.</li>
                  <li>Actionable icon fonts without accompanying visible text <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have a text alternative.</li>
                  <li>The alternative text for informative icon fonts <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be meaningful.</li>
                  <li>Decorative or redundant icon fonts <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> be set to <code>aria-hidden="true"</code>.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Download Summary & Checklist</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-linklist">
                  <li><a href="https://github.com/team-a11y/A11YPortal/blob/master/docs/summary-checklists/Images%2C%20Canvas%2C%20SVG%2C%20and%20Other%20Non-Text%20Content%20-%20Design%20-%20Summary%20and%20Checklist.pdf" class="link-ts"><span>Images, Canvas, SVG, and Other Non-Text Content PDF</span></a></li>
                </ul>

              </div>
              <div>
                <a href="https://dequeuniversity.com/class/images2/icon-font/" class="link-plug-on">
                  <span class="icon icon-college icon-xl icon-gray-dark mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></span> Icon Fonts - Deque University</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Tips & Tricks</h3>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>Strongly discouraged, use SVG instead</li>
                  <li>A11Y problems when fonts are replaced</li>
                </ul>

              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="col-md-5">

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Resources</h3>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Specifications</h4>
                <p>None documented</p>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Examples</h4>
                <p>None documented</p>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Miscellaneous</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-linklist">
                  <li><a href="http://ianfeather.co.uk/ten-reasons-we-switched-from-an-icon-font-to-svg/" class="link-ts"><span>Ten reasons we switched from an icon font to SVG</span></a></li>
                  <li><a href="https://speakerdeck.com/ninjanails/death-to-icon-fonts" class="link-ts"><span>Death to Icon Fonts</span></a></li>
                </ul>

              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Practice</h3>

