    <section class="full-cover bg-faded" role="region" id="html-5-canvas" aria-labelledby="title-html-5-canvas">
      <div class="container">

        <h2 class="full-cover-title" id="title-html-5-canvas">HTML 5 Canvas</h2>

        <div class="text-right to-top">
          <a href="#totop" class="link-ts"><span>To Top</span></a>
        </div>

        <div class="row">

          <div class="col-md-7">

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Checklist - Deque</h3>

                <h4 class="heading-s">HTML 5 <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-checklist">
                  <li>When <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> elements are used to display graphics, they <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be assigned <code>role="img"</code>.</li>
                  <li>All <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have a text alternative.</li>
                  <li>The alternative text for <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> be meaningful.</li>
                  <li>All <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> elements with complex images <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> have a detailed text alternative.</li>
                  <li>All <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> elements <span class="badge badge-info">SHOULD</span> have a background fill.</li>
                  <li>If text is required in a graphic, consider using SVG instead of <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code>.</li>
                  <li>A <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> element operable with mouse <span class="badge badge-success">MUST</span> also be keyboard accessible.</li>
                </ul>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Download Summary & Checklist</h4>
                <ul class="list-icons list-linklist">
                  <li><a href="https://github.com/team-a11y/A11YPortal/blob/master/docs/summary-checklists/Images%2C%20Canvas%2C%20SVG%2C%20and%20Other%20Non-Text%20Content%20-%20Design%20-%20Summary%20and%20Checklist.pdf" class="link-ts"><span>Images, Canvas, SVG, and Other Non-Text Content PDF</span></a></li>
                </ul>

              </div>
              <div>
                <a href="https://dequeuniversity.com/class/images2/canvas/" class="link-plug-on">
                  <span class="icon icon-college icon-xl icon-gray-dark mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></span> HTML 5 Canvas - Deque University</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Tips & Tricks</h3>
                <p>None documented</p>

              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="col-md-5">

            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-block">

                <h3 class="card-title">Resources</h3>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Specifications</h4>
                <p>None documented</p>

                <h4 class="heading-s">Examples</h4>
                <p>None documented</p>

